And He said, "That's small compared to what I'm about to do."As I was watching the Billy Graham revivals and the people coming down by the tens of thousands, the Lord said, "What I'm about to do is going to make this look like a little thing."Seeing them stand by the tens of thousands to come to Jesus.

00:32:57.200 --> 00:33:05.535
I have great anticipation as I pray with you all tonight, as I watch these great crusades with great auditoriums full of people.

00:33:05.536 --> 00:33:12.959
And the Lord said to me, "Tent revivals are coming back. Brush arbor churches are coming back.

00:33:12.960 --> 00:33:27.599
Holy Ghost Woodstocks are going to come back."And He talked to me about great security to bring stability in these meetings, having great law enforcement helping it.

00:33:27.600 --> 00:33:38.719
Because you're always going to have mass craziness where there is a great mass of people trying to do something good, as we saw what happened to our friend Charlie.

00:33:38.720 --> 00:33:43.359
There's always going to be some kind of evil trying to put out the flame.

00:33:43.360 --> 00:33:56.556
So, there'll be great key people, like I've talked to this week, that will have a great role in bringing stability and security to these meetings.

00:33:56.557 --> 00:34:04.939
I have an anticipation, and I hope you do, too. I hope it comes across by me talking to you tonight.

00:34:04.940 --> 00:34:12.715
What I'm anticipating, a great harvest of souls is coming, ladies and gentlemen, beyond what you've ever seen before.

00:34:12.716 --> 00:34:23.759
We saw something today with Charlie's funeral, where I thought there were probably 100,000 people plus there.

00:34:23.760 --> 00:34:34.142
That was a massive event, but it shows the level of where people are, that we're ready for change.

00:34:34.143 --> 00:34:44.920
We're ready for something. It's the birthing pains. Something is about to happen. So, what is our job in this?

00:34:44.921 --> 00:34:53.598
Our job is to pray, because I believe true revival does not take place without great prayer.

00:34:53.599 --> 00:34:57.731
Every revival has always been birthed out of a lot of prayer.

00:34:57.733 --> 00:35:10.990
From Azusa Street to Pensacola, for all these times, the Welsh revivals, and so on with John Wesley, all the greats—they were all birthed out of great prayer.

00:35:10.991 --> 00:35:17.197
And I believe that's what we're called to do. That's why He assembled us together for such a time as this.

00:35:17.198 --> 00:35:41.100
I don't believe it's by coincidence at all. I'm just telling you all, something major is about to take place.

00:35:41.101 --> 00:35:46.686
I've said it time and time again, but don't you feel that stirring?

00:35:46.687 --> 00:36:04.639
As I said last night, He told me, "This week marks something huge."And as I heard Nearer, My God, to Thee playing by those trumpets and those horns and the violins, I sat there in awe that He chose us.

00:36:04.640 --> 00:36:18.390
I sat there in awe that He chose you and I. We're the closers; He saved the best for last.

00:36:18.391 --> 00:36:30.036
He called each and every single one of us to be a great mouthpiece for Him in these last days. There's no one greater, there's no one too small.

00:36:30.037 --> 00:36:44.942
God will use every single one of us if we just have a yielded heart to Him and say, 'Here am I, Father. Send me.'I hope that encourages you.

00:36:44.943 --> 00:37:01.683
That part—I don't call it a program, this prayer service—those clips inspire me because I want to think big financially to get the gospel out big. You don't think small.

00:37:01.684 --> 00:37:14.959
If you think too small, it's just about 'my little church, my little friends, all this just to do what we've got to do.'No, you've got to think bigger.

00:37:14.960 --> 00:37:29.519
Stretch yourself. Stretch the way you believe. Stretch your capacity. Enlarge your tent today to think bigger today.

00:37:29.520 --> 00:37:44.319
When you see a sea of people, it's all hands on deck, for the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are truly few.

00:37:44.320 --> 00:37:50.528
So, let's take communion together. I always take communion before I pray.

00:37:50.529 --> 00:38:04.639
And it's like I told my new friend, this is something you should be doing with your family every single day of your life, for what I have seen coming.

00:38:04.640 --> 00:38:28.202
If you don't understand who you are in Christ—the Lord told me, He said, 'I want you—this is one of the main things I want you to teach My people, and make it a habit for them that they come before Me with communion on a day-to-day basis.'And I have done my best to show you the importance of taking communion.

00:38:28.203 --> 00:38:40.879
I don't look at it as a religious act; I look at this as relationship. I look at this as intimacy with my Friend.

00:38:40.880 --> 00:38:51.999
I don't look at it as doing something because it's required of me by a certain church, but I look at this as fellowship.

00:38:52.000 --> 00:39:03.358
This is me saying, 'Jesus, I just want to be closer to You.'This is what makes a marriage great.

00:39:03.359 --> 00:39:13.577
When you take communion with your wife and your kids, and you take your anointing oil like I do—this one's half gone, but I got this one from Billy Burke.

00:39:13.578 --> 00:39:21.197
This was special to me; He blessed me with this. He prayed over it and everything, and he blessed me, this Billy Burke.

00:39:21.198 --> 00:39:29.058
I'll even try to break it off and use what's in the rest of it when it's gone, but it's frankincense. It's really beautiful.

00:39:29.059 --> 00:39:41.679
But I anoint my head with oil with it all the time, and I anoint my kids with oil with this, and I touch their heads, and I pray over my children.

00:39:41.680 --> 00:39:47.634
But you anoint your kids with oil. You anoint your family with oil, and you pray over them.

00:39:47.635 --> 00:39:58.639
And the anointing oil represents a bloodline. And where the blood is applied, Satan cannot cross if you believe it.

00:39:58.640 --> 00:40:07.048
It's not something religious that you do; it's what it represents in the spirit realm.

00:40:07.049 --> 00:40:25.439
When Moses came before the children of Israel and said, 'I want you to sacrifice a lamb and put the blood upon your doorpost so that the death angel will not come into your house and destroy your firstborn.

00:40:25.440 --> 00:40:45.519
But the blood will be applied to the doorpost to represent the blood of the lamb, so that death can't come in your home.'And as you do it today, it's saying the blood covers it and the death angel's not going to touch me either.

00:40:45.520 --> 00:40:58.408
The demonic can't touch me either. I apply the blood over the doorposts of my home, and no satanic agenda can come near me or my wife or my children.

00:40:58.409 --> 00:41:07.598
I put it on my pocketbook. I put it on my wallet. I say, 'No weapon formed against my finances will prosper.

00:41:07.599 --> 00:41:15.779
Every tongue that rises against me will be condemned. I have goodness and mercy following me all the days of my life.

00:41:15.780 --> 00:41:20.055
I am protected by the blood of the Lamb.'I anoint my throat with oil.

00:41:20.056 --> 00:41:24.531
I anoint my body. And even if I'm not—I'm not moved by what I see.

00:41:24.532 --> 00:41:36.879
I'm not moved by what I feel. I'm moved by what the word of God says. And if God be for me, who can be against me?

00:41:36.880 --> 00:41:42.905
Regardless of what's being—even with a symptom like I have, you go, 'I don't care what the symptoms say.

00:41:42.906 --> 00:41:50.559
I'm not moved by what I see. I'm not moved by what I feel. I'm moved by what the word of God says.

00:41:50.560 --> 00:42:01.279
By His stripes, I am healed.'Even if my flesh doesn't totally agree with it right now, I'm not moved by what my flesh does.

00:42:01.280 --> 00:42:12.879
I'm not moved by how my flesh feels. You're going to shut up, flesh, and I'm going to pray with these people tonight.

00:42:12.880 --> 00:42:28.799
You've got to be bigger than your flesh screaming to you and saying, 'Well, you don't feel good.'No, I feel great! Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:42:28.800 --> 00:42:39.838
Regardless of what your flesh tries to tell you, I'm not moved by what the flesh says; I'm moved by what the Spirit says and what this beautiful book says.

00:42:39.839 --> 00:42:47.838
That's what I'm moved by, and that's where you have to be moved by, especially in the days of what I've seen coming.

00:42:47.839 --> 00:42:53.630
I'm not moved by what I see on the news. I'm not moved by the terror at night.

00:42:53.631 --> 00:42:59.759
I'm not moved by the plague. I'm not moved by all these things, because a plague is coming.

00:42:59.760 --> 00:43:17.139
And the Lord said, 'You must take your prayer times more seriously, and pray for these people, and get them prepared for what's coming, that you stand as a watchman on the wall and warn them, that they learn to take communion and understand who they are.'Remember what I told you.

00:43:17.140 --> 00:43:34.559
If you do not understand Psalm 91, if you do not understand and have a revelation of Psalm 23 in the days ahead, you are not going to make it. You must understand who you are.

00:43:34.560 --> 00:43:47.563
You must understand the power of the covenant of what this represents—that it's not just a cup of juice and a wafer, a little cup and wafer.

00:43:47.564 --> 00:44:01.166
This represents something; it's relationship. Jesus Christ paid the price for you to walk in healing and wholeness and wellness in your life.

00:44:01.167 --> 00:44:14.564
Jesus Christ became sickness and disease; He became poor so that you might be rich through His poverty—not just monetarily, but spirit, soul, and body.

00:44:14.565 --> 00:44:22.078
Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:44:22.079 --> 00:44:43.199
And I even told somebody recently, 'If you're not prosperous in your soul, you're not going to be prosperous in your health all the time.'You've got to renew your mind, your will, and your emotions to the word of God, because if you do not, the devourer is at your door.

00:44:43.200 --> 00:44:48.631
And I have to do exactly what I'm preaching to you tonight all the time, too. Brandon's not an exception.

00:44:48.632 --> 00:44:58.203
Well, you know, no, seriously, the Lord told me, He said, 'You know what you sound like tonight?'And I was whining about everything that I went through last week.

00:44:58.204 --> 00:45:03.657
He said, 'You sound like Elijah over there crying at the cave.'You know, 'Oh, everything's so bad.

00:45:03.658 --> 00:45:19.279
Jezebel's after me.'But He said, 'You haven't gone to the point of saying that you just want Me to take you home like he did.'He said, 'But Brandon, what you say out of your mouth is important.

00:45:19.280 --> 00:45:25.809
What you say out of your mouth is important, for life and death is in the power of your tongue, son.

00:45:25.810 --> 00:45:52.889
All that mealy-mouthed and all that stuff you're saying right now, watch what you're saying.'He said, 'I want to open your eyes to something.'And as I was interceding and feeling sorry for myself for the week that I had, He said, 'Give your angels something to work with right now, and I want to show you.'And I saw them fighting in the spirit realm, and I saw they had Captain America shields.

00:45:52.890 --> 00:46:00.907
These angels were fighting and they had Captain America shields—the round ones—and they had swords, and they were up there battling.

00:46:00.908 --> 00:46:11.596
And He said, 'Give them something to work with in the spirit realm.'And I said, 'Well, how do I do that?'He said, 'Quote the scripture concerning what you're going through.

00:46:11.597 --> 00:46:23.464
Quote the scripture. Use the sword of the Spirit. Quote the fiery word out of your mouth. Be a believing believer and not a doubter.

00:46:23.465 --> 00:46:30.159
You're an overcomer by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of your testimony.'Do you understand?

00:46:30.160 --> 00:46:34.072
You're not moved by what you see. You're not moved by what you feel.

00:46:34.073 --> 00:46:42.719
You're moved by what the word says. Now stand up and be who I've called you to be.

00:46:42.720 --> 00:46:58.793
You can either be mealy-mouthed, limp-wristed, and feel sorry for yourself, or you can be bold as a lion and say, "Thus far, Satan, and no further."It is written.

00:46:58.794 --> 00:47:22.836
It is written, "Greater is he that is in me than he that is in the world."It is written, "A thousand shall fall at my side and 10,000 at my right hand, but nothing shall come nigh me."That's where you have to stand.

00:47:22.837 --> 00:47:51.519
And when the Lord showed me that, I felt when I started, I told Diana, I said, "Babe, go get that book that lady gave us, and quote those scriptures until we feel better."She goes, "How many times are we going to read them?"I said, "Until we feel better."The word will work if you work it.

00:47:51.520 --> 00:47:56.078
I said, "It don't matter how many times, hun. Even until we get tired.

00:47:56.079 --> 00:48:16.558
We quote these scriptures until they become real to us."It becomes a Rhema word on the inside of you that is not just "Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star."It's not "how I wonder what you are,"because that's what a lot of it is when you just read something for the first time.

00:48:16.559 --> 00:48:32.318
But when it becomes Rhema to you is when it becomes real to you and has gone down so deep inside of you that there's no devil in hell that can talk you out of what he said he would do for you.

00:48:32.319 --> 00:48:36.573
There's no devil in hell that can try to convince you that you're not saved.

00:48:36.574 --> 00:48:41.358
Is that right? Some of you would fight it with all your heart.

00:48:41.359 --> 00:48:46.239
That devil tells you you're not saved. "Oh, I know I'm saved.

00:48:46.240 --> 00:48:51.759
How dare you? I'm born again by the blood of Jesus Christ. I'm born again.

00:48:51.760 --> 00:48:55.626
My name's written in the Lamb's Book of Life. Get out of here, devil.

00:48:55.627 --> 00:49:07.999
I know I'm saved."But when he comes and tells you your son's not going to make it, your son's going to serve the devil, he has a plan—the devil has a plan for your son.

00:49:08.000 --> 00:49:16.558
"Oh, the devil's going to take your son. He's going to do witchcraft. He's going to do all..."The devil's got a plan for your son.

00:49:16.559 --> 00:49:39.679
You believe it because you don't realize that he said, "Train up a child in the way they should go, and when they get older, they'll not depart from it."Regardless of how Johnny or whoever is acting right now, my God said that my children will be my offspring.

00:49:39.680 --> 00:49:43.619
The fruit of my offspring, the fruit of my children will be blessed.

00:49:43.620 --> 00:49:47.759
They're going to be blessed. They're going to be blessed coming in.

00:49:47.760 --> 00:49:52.094
They're going to be blessed coming out. My children will serve God.

00:49:52.095 --> 00:50:04.190
My children will be on fire for God. My children will not go to hell. And that's where you have to stand.

00:50:04.191 --> 00:50:11.936
Even when those kids are acting really bad, I'm training my child up in the way they should go.

00:50:11.937 --> 00:50:22.427
My kids know about Jesus. The seed of righteousness is inside of them, even if they're not displaying it right now. Now, I anoint them with oil. I anoint where they sleep.

00:50:22.428 --> 00:50:33.833
They may act rebellious in who they're hanging out with, and I might need to take a rod and spank their heinie a little bit because the Bible said if you spare the rod, you spoil the child.

00:50:33.834 --> 00:50:42.301
And it's not abuse; it's love. But either way, we're going to walk in love up in here.

00:50:42.302 --> 00:50:53.679
And love corrects. Love disciplines, not abuse. It didn't say beat them when you're angry. That's wrong.

00:50:53.680 --> 00:51:02.473
It's like I heard Kim Clement say, "If you're always chastising your kids, you're an idiot."That's not smart.

00:51:02.474 --> 00:51:09.362
God doesn't chastise all the time. Always talking about God bringing judgment on things—God's not always judging and being mad.

00:51:09.363 --> 00:51:17.722
I'm going to be real with y'all. God's not angry. God's not up there always conspiring against you.

00:51:17.723 --> 00:51:29.679
You think he's, you know, "What is he doing today, Jesus? I think I'll slap him in the head with something."I realize that God is a God of love.

00:51:29.680 --> 00:51:33.610
God is not conspiring up there thinking how he's going to make your life miserable.

00:51:33.611 --> 00:51:51.039
"Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers."Above all things, everything for you to have a good and expected end.

00:51:51.040 --> 00:52:07.519
That's a good God. But most people think God's up there mad, and he's mad at America, boy, he's mad at Israel, he's mad at Thailand, he's mad at China, he's mad...

00:52:07.520 --> 00:52:17.554
No, God's not mad. Now, what does the Bible say? Seedtime and harvest never cease.

00:52:17.555 --> 00:52:22.393
Whatsoever a man sows, that will he also reap. Is that what the Bible says?

00:52:22.394 --> 00:52:28.959
As long as the earth remains, seedtime and harvest will always exist.

00:52:28.960 --> 00:52:35.039
As long as the earth remains, you can plant a seed in that ground.

00:52:35.040 --> 00:52:41.638
You can plant a seed in that ground, and if you water it and the sun hits it, it's going to grow.

00:52:41.639 --> 00:52:53.377
You can plant a seed in your wife, and you'll reap a baby. You can plant a seed in the church offering, and you're going to reap a harvest.

00:52:53.378 --> 00:53:11.699
Seedtime and harvest always work. I believe it. So because we live in a fallen world and you sow bad seed, you reap the harvest of that.

00:53:11.700 --> 00:53:23.279
So we are going to see, because seedtime and harvest is accelerated, the sowers and the reapers are going to go hand in hand like we've been told.

00:53:23.280 --> 00:53:31.118
And because of this acceleration, you're about to see seedtime and harvest like you've never seen it before.

00:53:31.119 --> 00:53:40.399
And when you see people sow to the flesh, they'll reap of the flesh, and when you sow to the spirit, they'll reap of the spirit.

00:53:40.400 --> 00:53:45.855
So, we're about to see things that you never thought you would see because time is short.

00:53:45.856 --> 00:53:50.558
And you're going to see things in the earth like you've never seen.

00:53:50.559 --> 00:54:07.679
You're going to see because the earth is crying out, the cup of sin is full, and the seedtime and harvest of that's full, and you're about to see tribulation for the seeds that were sown, and we've never seen anything like it before.

00:54:07.680 --> 00:54:18.276
The full manifestation of the seeds that were sown are going to be reaped all at one time. And God's wrath will be poured out upon this earth.

00:54:18.277 --> 00:54:24.619
And you're going to see it, and it's going to be like, "Oh my goodness."That's what people—if you don't get born again, is what I'm going to say.

00:54:24.620 --> 00:54:47.679
But what we're also going to see is, I told you, great revival, great harvest, healings, demonstrations, manifestations of the glory right before the catching away of the church. I just believe it with all my heart.

00:54:47.680 --> 00:55:08.239
So, I hope you get excited about what we're about to see and have an anticipation for God to get even your neighbors saved, to get your daughters and your sons saved, to have revival in your homes, for husbands and wives to come together with great...

00:55:08.240 --> 00:55:11.687
"You know what, devil? We're going to punch you in the head today as a unit.

00:55:11.688 --> 00:55:17.439
We're going to be more in love. We're going to walk in love. We're going to have more friendship up in here.

00:55:17.440 --> 00:55:20.916
We're going to pray together. We're going to read the Bible together.

00:55:20.917 --> 00:55:23.959
And we're going to be more of a unit together than ever before.

00:55:23.960 --> 00:55:42.318
And we're not going to allow the devil to come in and rob our marriage through strife, through bitterness, through whatever."The Lord told me, he said, "As the days approach, Brandon, you must make sure strife, if it ever exists, as a minimum, do not allow it in your home ever.

00:55:42.319 --> 00:55:56.078
Always diffuse it at all cost. It's not worth it. Make sure love is a pillar in your home.

00:55:56.079 --> 00:56:10.479
Do not allow strife in at all costs. It's not worth it."So hopefully this helps you tonight.

00:56:10.480 --> 00:56:18.713
It's just stuff that we're dealing with, and that's what Diana and I talk about.

00:56:18.714 --> 00:56:33.118
It's what prepares us to make sure that we're walking in, and we have our t's crossed and our i's doted, and you're ready, and you have your eyes peeled.

00:56:33.119 --> 00:56:36.747
It's like talking to people, and they say, "I watch the crowd.

00:56:36.748 --> 00:56:41.357
I watch this."Yes, I'm a people watcher, too. I hear them. I never let my guard down.

00:56:41.358 --> 00:56:45.576
Yes, I know. But we've got to have times of infilling and refreshing, too.

00:56:45.577 --> 00:57:01.838
We must have a time to drink from the Father and to make sure our cup is full of oil, our lamps are full, our lives are full and ready so that the enemy is not able to come and eat our lunch.

00:57:01.839 --> 00:57:12.318
He looks for the weak ones that are separated from the fold. The wolf does. Remember, the wolf is looking for the weak and sick ones.

00:57:12.319 --> 00:57:17.304
He doesn't go after the strong ones that have the full meat and are ready to fight.

00:57:17.305 --> 00:57:23.279
He looks for the ones that look like they're malnourished and off to the side of the fold.

00:57:23.280 --> 00:57:30.274
'Can I take him out? Can I take you out?'Does that make sense?

00:57:30.275 --> 00:57:42.318
You don't go after the strong ones; you go after the weak ones. So I want you to remain strong.

00:57:42.319 --> 00:57:50.559
I want you to remain strong and make this your best friend—the word of God in these last days.

00:57:50.560 --> 00:58:02.131
I even told certain folks I talked to, 'You must read Psalms 91 and Psalms 23 more and more and more.'You must know this.

00:58:02.132 --> 00:58:13.279
You must understand the power of communion. You must understand this: the meal that heals.

00:58:13.280 --> 00:58:19.039
It's so important, ladies and gentlemen. It's so important.

00:58:19.040 --> 00:58:33.902
I tell you this, and it's like I say all the time, if what you're doing is not working and you keep going down the same road all the time expecting different results, it's insanity. Try something new.

00:58:33.903 --> 00:58:50.264
That's why Diana and I, when we come to Megan and we do the therapies for Megan, if we didn't see results within the first 100 days because our budgets were limited, you don't keep doing the same thing expecting different results.

00:58:50.265 --> 00:58:59.999
After a point of time, you realize this isn't bearing any fruit. It's time to change directions.

00:59:00.000 --> 00:59:16.558
So if you don't have different fruit in your life after a while, and you don't see first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation—even a little bit of change with even coming and praying with me—then do something different.

00:59:16.559 --> 00:59:21.118
I do not want to be something that is a stumbling block for anybody.

00:59:21.119 --> 00:59:35.519
If you don't see change from praying with me and the things that I'm telling you, and it's not causing you to grow from glory to glory, then find something that does.

00:59:35.520 --> 00:59:47.768
Then find something that does, because we have to change from glory to glory. The word must change you from the inside out.

00:59:47.769 --> 00:59:55.439
If it is not, you're becoming stagnant and the enemy will devour you, especially with what I've seen coming.

00:59:55.440 --> 01:00:01.626
You must hear me. The Lord said, 'Remember, I was driving down...'I'll tell you where I was.

01:00:01.627 --> 01:00:12.016
I was on I-35 and Covell Road in Edmond, Oklahoma. You can look it up—I-35 and Covell Road.

01:00:12.017 --> 01:00:20.394
And there's a Starbucks there and a Braum's there. And there's a field over here with a Showtime Cinema Theater.

01:00:20.395 --> 01:00:31.358
I exited off that road. I took a right and I was going down the road to go to the post office.

01:00:31.359 --> 01:00:45.677
And the Lord spoke to me when I got off that road that day, and he said to me, 'Brandon, very sobering days are coming. Very sobering days are coming to the church.

01:00:45.678 --> 01:01:00.773
Sobering days are coming to the world.'And he said, 'But what's the opposite of sober?'And I said, 'Lord, drunk is.'And he said, 'Yes.

01:01:00.774 --> 01:01:06.407
Be being filled with the Holy Spirit to overflowing like a bubbling, bubbling, bubbling, bubbling.

01:01:06.408 --> 01:01:13.769
